column5: Heading to port dalhousie tonight to try for some Browns.  Keeping Martindale pond as a backup plan, however I have never been to martindale so looking for a good spot to sit along the water and fish.  I checked google earth and it seems the best place is henley island but I am not sure that place is accessible since the yacht club is there.  Thanks
Thanks.  I will keep that in mind for next time I head out to Port D.
